[{"id":"RAW_e73edd69","title":"我们如何在一周内用 AI 重构 Next.js","link":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/vinext/","date":"2026-02-24 20:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_e73edd69.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Cloudflare Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_3879b2af","title":"1500 个 PR、0 人写代码：Codex 驱动的百万行级内部产品实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651276192&idx=2&sn=3cbb6109e944e9fb09f0037d5b5b6172","date":"2026-02-24 10:09:00","oneSentenceSummary":"OpenAI 揭秘其内部实验：通过 Codex Agent 驱动，在 5 个月内实现了 0 人工代码、百万行规模的产品开发，重新定义了 AI 时代的软件工程范式。","summary":"文章详细记录了 OpenAI 团队的一项激进实验：在 5 个月内利用 Codex（由 GPT-5 驱动）开发出一款完全没有人工编写代码的百万行级内部产品。核心发现是，当工程师从“代码编写者”转变为“环境与反馈循环设计师”时，研发效率可提升至传统模式的 10 倍。文章深入探讨了如何通过增强应用的可读性（如接入 DevTools 和可观测性栈）赋能 Agent，如何利用“地图式”文档管理上下文，以及如何通过极其严格的架构约束和自动化的“垃圾回收”机制来对抗 AI 生成代码带来的熵增。这一实践为未来“AI 原生”的软件工程提供了极具价值的蓝图。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3879b2af.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":95},{"id":"RAW_3308e250","title":"智谱 GLM-5 技术全公开！完全适配华为等国产芯片，美国网友酸了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/381712.html","date":"2026-02-23 05:19:44","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3308e250.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c16f8d46","title":"容器运行时迁移有大坑！Netflix 的 CPU 架构瓶颈排查与修复实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMjYzNjkzNw==&mid=2247634629&idx=1&sn=cca8c23b8cb9ef41ee85d53e4ca8bf66","date":"2026-02-24 23:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c16f8d46.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"dbaplus社群","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_97909516","title":"知识引导","link":"https://martinfowler.com/articles/reduce-friction-ai/knowledge-priming.html","date":"2026-02-24 14:40:00"